          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 78645,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Bisher haben wir gelernt, wie man eine <code>while</code>-Schleife erstellt. Jetzt konzentrieren wir uns darauf, wie man verhindert, dass sie unendlich schleifen.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Creating the variable",
            "id": 78648,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um eine Schleife zu stoppen, beginnen wir damit, eine Variable außerhalb der Schleife zu erstellen.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"10\" /><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\":\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>keep_going</code>, gefolgt von <code>=</code> und schließlich <code>True</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Variable in the condition",
            "id": 78647,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Wir verwenden die Variable in der Bedingung, um zu entscheiden, ob die Schleife ihren Codeblock ausführen soll oder nicht. Zum Beispiel, <code>keep_going == True</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keep_going == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option startIndex=\"36\" endIndex=\"38\" /><option startIndex=\"39\" endIndex=\"43\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>keep_going</code>, gefolgt von <code>==</code> und schließlich <code>True</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Updating the variable",
            "id": 78670,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Innerhalb des Codeblocks stoppen wir die Schleife, indem wir <code>keep_going</code> auf <code>False</code> setzen, sodass die Bedingung <code>False</code> zurückgibt.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keep_going == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  keep_going = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"81\" endIndex=\"86\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Gib <code>False</code> ein.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Stopping the loop",
            "id": 78644,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Die Schleife führt ihren gesamten Codeblock aus, weil <code>keep_going</code> zunächst <code>True</code> ist, aber sie wird nicht erneut ausgeführt, wenn wir <code>keep_going</code> auf <code>False</code> setzen.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keep_going == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  keep_going = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;one more time&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"one more time\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Creating the variable",
            "id": 78643,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Woher wissen wir, dass diese Schleife läuft und nie aufhört, ihren Codeblock zu wiederholen?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"load_data = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loading data..&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Loading data..\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loading data..\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loading data..\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Es gibt keine Variable in der Bedingung</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Diese Schleife wird nicht ausgeführt, da die Bedingung <code>False</code> ist</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Es gibt keine Variable in der Bedingung.</p></body></html>"
          },
