            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Woher wissen wir, dass diese Schleife stoppt?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keep_going == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Just keep swimming&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  keep_going = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Just keep swimming\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Die <code>keep_going</code>-Variable wird innerhalb des Codeblocks auf <code>False</code> aktualisiert</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Wir wissen nicht, ob die Schleife stoppt</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Die <code>keep_going</code>-Variable wird innerhalb des Codeblocks auf <code>False</code> aktualisiert.</p></body></html>"
