            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Erstelle eine Variable für die <code>while</code>-Schleife.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_playing = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keep_playing == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Now Playing: Ryan Paris&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  keep_playing = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"10\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Now Playing: Ryan Paris\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>keep_playing</code>, gefolgt von <code>=</code> und schließlich <code>True</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
